{"tid":834681,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩比出了「手指愛心」！網友看了直呼「好可愛！」","createTime":"2018-09-24T10:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T17:27:03.000Z","uid":9573,"like":20,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c270e4fd95e60a1d1a311c3b6e3568733e013c29","tid":834681,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:45:09.000Z","msg":"日前南北兩韓峰會結束，傳出當時文在寅夫婦和金正恩夫婦在白頭山合影時，文在寅邀請金正恩一起比出南韓流行的「手指愛心」，沒想到當時金正恩竟然比不出來。不過現在南韓總統府青瓦台也公布當時照片，只見金正恩粗粗的手指還是成功地比出了「手指愛心」，但看起來就是和別人不一樣，讓不少網友看了直呼「好可愛！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3ytLNGOdHbGDPQe.M8q_.w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzE1/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/a09510ba7db2da4282212fece25cdc63\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3ytLNGOdHbGDPQe.M8q_.w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzE1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fa09510ba7db2da4282212fece25cdc63&h=1802ae2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲金正恩（右二）成功比出手指愛心。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報導，南韓青瓦台發言人金宜謙表示，當文在寅邀請金正恩比出「手指愛心」時，金正恩一看便驚呼，「你是怎麼辦到的？我完全比不出來」，當時報導傳出，金正恩最終靠著太太李雪主的幫忙下，終於做到了。現在青瓦台也PO出當時照片，只見金正恩將大拇指和食指微微交叉，但似乎手指太粗，做起來不是很明顯，最後他只能尷尬地朝著鏡頭另一側傻笑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170604/photo/bkn-20170604130021829-0604_00862_001_03p.jpg?20170604172705\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170604%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170604130021829-0604_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20170604172705&h=e173a737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片一出，立刻掀起熱議，網友紛紛留言表示，「金正恩的心看起來有點尷尬喔」、「真沒辦法想像這輩子竟然看得到金正恩的手指愛心」、「千雪看起來好萌喔」，還有人說，「可惡！李雪主捧住金正恩的手指愛心的時候，畫面看起來好可愛！」"},{"pid":"640a620e199c2fba6a99abb1b049d7b708578a02","tid":834681,"uid":49391,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:20:35.000Z","msg":"成功過底,跟左新大佬,係精神嘅<br />\n中共成日以恩人自居,對佢頤指氣使,佢都忍夠啦"},{"pid":"51708742790aca2ccbe778c565e3c5d6d4172390","tid":834681,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"佢老婆做咩要托住佢隻手？"},{"pid":"8d0710844309ccbea3b1e16514ca783a7c30a1ec","tid":834681,"uid":10876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"文在寅邀請金正恩一起比出南韓流行的「手指愛心」<br />\nGay<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b3d0e738a60ba3b784afa4ffe587bb9a4bbf36","tid":834681,"uid":59163,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"正平比千雪bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95280f2102bda292967609e2389abfde9ff138a0","tid":834681,"uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"51708742790aca2ccbe778c565e3c5d6d4172390","tid":834681,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"佢老婆做咩要托住佢隻手？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"傳統婦女美德以夫為重,唔會走去搞個人特色"},{"pid":"a2f9442b1ed806e79ab625ed8c1e8c0659adb58b","tid":834681,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95280f2102bda292967609e2389abfde9ff138a0","tid":834681,"uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"51708742790aca2ccbe778c565e3c5d6d4172390","tid":834681,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"佢老婆做咩要托住佢隻手？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"傳統婦女美德以夫為重,唔會走去搞個人特色"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd987bdffb4d7738774aee8263ef60c43d05b016","tid":834681,"uid":815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"有千雪BB就正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1334e5ab3d128760cd412d436aff2cfe989b4216","tid":834681,"uid":59898,"like":0